criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Septic patients in Department of Critical Care Medicine, Guangdong Provincial Hospital
             of Chinese Medicine;

          2. APACHE-Ⅱ score greater than 15 points;

          3. Signing the informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Fasting patients in the clinical, such as digestive tract perforation, bleeding or
             postoperative patients with gastrointestinal tract;

          2. Allergic to enteral nutrition preparations;

          3. Don't want to attend the test or not with the healer.
